msgid "[[!meta title=\"Tails 3.0 will require a 64-bit processor\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Tails 3.0 requerirà un processador de 64 bits\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!tag announce]]\n"
msgstr "[[!tag announce]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Tails 3.0 will require a 64-bit <span\n"
"class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia x86-64]]</span> compatible processor.\n"
"As opposed to older versions of Tails, it will not work on\n"
"32-bit processors.\n"
msgstr ""
"Tails 3.0 requerirà un processador de 64 bits compatible amb\n"
"<span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia_ca Arquitectura_x86-64 desc=\"x86-"
"64\"]]</span>.\n"
"A diferència de les versions anteriors de Tails, no funcionarà\n"
"per a processadors de 32 bits.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We have waited for years until we felt it was the right time to do this "
"switch. Still, this was a hard decision for us to make. Today, we want to "
"explain why we eventually made this decision, how it will affect users, and "
"when."
msgstr ""
"Hem esperat durant anys fins que hem sentit que era el moment adequat per "
"fer aquest canvi. Tot i així, ha sigut una decisió difícil de prendre per a "
"nosaltres. Avui volem explicar per què finalment hem pres aquesta decisió, "
"com afectarà els usuaris i quan."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "When will this transition happen?"
msgstr "Quan es produirà aquesta transició?"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Our current goal is to release Tails 3.0, and stop supporting computers with "
"a 32-bit processor, on **June 13, 2017**."
msgstr ""
"El nostre objectiu actual és llançar Tails 3.0 i deixar de donar suport als "
"ordinadors amb un processador de 32 bits el **13 de juny de 2017**."

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Will Tails still work on this computer?"
msgstr "Tails encara funcionarà en aquest ordinador?"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Here is the quickest way to find out:"
msgstr "Aquí teniu la manera més ràpida d'esbrinar-ho:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Start Tails."
msgstr "Inicieu Tails."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Choose <span class=\"menuchoice\"><span class=\"guimenu\">Applications</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guisubmenu\">Utilities</span>&nbsp;▸ <span "
"class=\"guimenuitem\">Terminal</span></span> to open a terminal."
msgstr ""
"Trieu <span class=\"menuchoice\"><span class=\"guimenu\">Aplicacions</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guisubmenu\">Utilitats</span>&nbsp;▸ <span "
"class=\"guimenuitem\">Terminal</span></span> per obrir un terminal."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Execute the following command to display system information:"
msgstr "Executeu l'ordre següent per mostrar la informació del sistema:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "           uname -m\n"
msgstr "           uname -m\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Then, there are two possible cases:"
msgstr "Aleshores, hi ha dos casos possibles:"

#. type: Bullet: '   * '
msgid ""
"If you see `x86_64`, then you're good: Tails 3.0 should work fine on this "
"computer. But the best way to be 100% sure is to try one of the test "
"versions of Tails 3.0. One was released last November, and a new one should "
"be published later this week, so: stay tuned!"
msgstr ""
"Si veieu `x86_64`, aleshores esteu bé: Tails 3.0 hauria de funcionar bé en "
"aquest ordinador. Però la millor manera d'estar 100% segur és provar una de "
"les versions de prova de Tails 3.0. Una es va publicar el novembre passat, i "
"una de nova s'hauria de publicar a finals d'aquesta setmana, així que: "
"estigueu atent!"

#. type: Bullet: '   * '
msgid ""
"Else, if you see `i686`, then we have bad news: Tails 3.0 will *not* work on "
"this computer. You now have four and a half months to find a computer with a "
"64-bit processor. Sorry, and good luck with that!"
msgstr ""
"En cas contrari, si veieu `i686`, tenim una mala notícia: Tails 3.0 *no* "
"funcionarà en aquest ordinador. Ara teniu quatre mesos i mig per trobar un "
"ordinador amb un processador de 64 bits. Ho sentim, i molta sort amb això!"

#. type: Title #
#, no-wrap
msgid "Why this change?"
msgstr "Per què aquest canvi?"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"It's no surprise that over the last years, the number of people who use "
"Tails on a 32-bit computer [[!tails_ticket 8183 desc=\"has dropped\"]]: most "
"32-bit computers are at least ten years old, and one after the other their "
"hardware stops working. As a result, in the beginning of 2016, [[!toggle "
"id=\"stats\" text=\"only 4%\"]] of Tails users were still using a 32-bit "
"computer."
msgstr ""
"No és d'estranyar que durant els últims anys, el nombre de persones que "
"utilitzen Tails en un ordinador de 32 bits [[!tails_ticket 8183 desc=\"ha "
"caigut\"]]: la majoria dels ordinadors de 32 bits tenen almenys deu anys i "
"un després de l'altre, el seu maquinari deixa de funcionar. Com a resultat, "
"a principis de 2016, [[!toggle id=\"stats\" text=\"només el 4%\"]] dels "
"usuaris de Tails encara utilitzaven un ordinador de 32 bits."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[[!toggleable id=\"stats\" text=\"\"\"These statistics are gathered from bug "
"reports we have received from [[WhisperBack|doc/first_steps/"
"whisperback#whisperback]].\"\"\"]]"
msgstr ""
"[[!toggleable id=\"stats\" text=\"\"\"Aquestes estadístiques es recullen a "
"partir dels informes d'errors que hem rebut de [[WhisperBack|doc/first_steps/"
"whisperback#whisperback]].\"\"\"]]"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Of course, some of these computers will keep working for a while. But once "
"the number had fallen this low, the benefits of switching Tails to 64-bit "
"outweighed the reasons we had to keep supporting 32-bit computers."
msgstr ""
"Per descomptat, alguns d'aquests ordinadors seguiran funcionant durant un "
"temps. Però una vegada que el nombre va baixar tan baix, els avantatges de "
"canviar Tails a 64 bits van superar els motius pels quals havíem de "
"continuar donant suport a ordinadors de 32 bits."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "We had two main reasons to switch Tails to 64-bit:"
msgstr "Teníem dos motius principals per canviar Tails a 64 bits:"

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"**We want Tails users to be safer**: software built for 64-bit processors "
"can benefit from several improvements that make it harder for attackers to "
"exploit security vulnerabilities (improved [[!wikipedia Address space layout "
"randomization]], compulsory support for the [[!wikipedia NX bit]])."
msgstr ""
"**Volem que els usuaris de Tails estiguin més segurs**: el programari creat "
"per a processadors de 64 bits pot beneficiar-se de diverses millores que "
"dificulten l'explotació de vulnerabilitats de seguretat per als atacants ([[!"
"wikipedia Address space layout randomization desc=\"aleatorització millorada "
"de la disposició de l'espai d'adreces\"]], suport obligatori per al [[!"
"wikipedia NX bit]])."

#. type: Bullet: '* '
msgid ""
"**We want to our project to be (more) sustainable**: Tails has been using a "
"64-bit Linux kernel for a while on machines that support it.  But all other "
"programs included in Tails so far were built for 32-bit processors, and "
"compatibility issues kept arising. In the last few years, the developers who "
"maintain Tails have spent lots of time addressing such issues. We would "
"rather see them spend their time in ways that benefit our users on the long "
"term, and not on problems that will vanish when Tails switches to 64-bit "
"eventually."
msgstr ""
"**Volem que el nostre projecte sigui (més) sostenible**: Tails fa temps que "
"utilitza un nucli Linux de 64 bits en màquines que el suporten. Però tots "
"els altres programes inclosos a Tails fins ara s'han creat per a "
"processadors de 32 bits i han sorgit problemes de compatibilitat. En els "
"últims anys, els desenvolupadors que mantenen Tails han dedicat molt de "
"temps abordant aquests problemes. Preferim veure'ls passar el temps de "
"manera que beneficiï els nostres usuaris a llarg termini, i no en problemes "
"que desapareixeran quan Tails canviï a 64 bits."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Thanks for your attention, and sorry for the inconvenience it may cause to "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Gràcies per la vostra atenció, i disculpeu les molèsties que us pugui "
"ocasionar."
